             was indicted for <rs id="t18180617-46-off254" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180617-46-off254" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180617-46-off254" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18180617-46-cd255" type="crimeDate">24th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180617-46-off254 t18180617-46-cd255"></join>, one jacket, value 4s.; one waistcoat, value 2s., and one pair of trowsers, value 3s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18180617-46-victim437" type="victimName">
                     Peter 
                     Bews
                  <interp inst="t18180617-46-victim437" type="surname" value="Bews"></interp>
